ang trải nghi&ecirc;̣m trực ti&ecirc;́p tại rạp hát.</p>\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" title=\"c&ocirc;ng nghệ ClearAudio+ tr&ecirc;n Android Tivi Sony 4K 43 inch KD-43X7500F\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/1942/158930/tivi-sony-kd-43x7500f-7.jpg\" alt=\"c&ocirc;ng nghệ ClearAudio+ tr&ecirc;n Android Tivi Sony 4K 43 inch KD-43X7500F\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/1942/158930/tivi-sony-kd-43x7500f-7.jpg\" /></p>\n<h3>Hệ điều h&agrave;nh Android dễ sử dụng</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Android tivi Sony\" href=\"https://www.dienmayxanh.com/tivi-sony?g=android-tivi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Android tivi Sony</a>&nbsp;chạy tr&ecirc;n hệ điều h&agrave;nh&nbsp;<a title=\"Android\" href=\"https://www.dienmayxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/cac-dong-android-tivi-tren-thi-truong-hien-nay-co-732394\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Android</a>&nbsp;7.0 quen thu&ocirc;̣c dễ sử dụng cùng nhi&ecirc;̀u ứng dụng giải trí h&acirc;́p d&acirc;̃n: Tr&igrave;nh duyệt Web, Youtube, Zing TV, Netflix, Nhạc của tui, Game Asphalt 8, ClipTV... giúp bạn có những phút gi&acirc;y giải trí thoải mái ngay tại nhà.</p>\n<div class=\"fluid-width-video-wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XGHovz80S3U\" name=\"fitvid0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\n<h3>Chi&ecirc;́u màn hình đi&ecirc;̣n thoại l&ecirc;n tivi với t&iacute;nh năng Screen Mirroring</h3>\n<p><img class=\"lazy\" title=\"Chi&ecirc;́u màn hình đi&ecirc;̣n thoại l&ecirc;n Android Tivi Sony 4K 43 inch KD-43X7500F\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/1942/158930/tivi-sony-kd-43x7500f-5.jpg\" alt=\"Chi&ecirc;́u màn hình đi&ecirc;̣n thoại l&ecirc;n Android Tivi Sony 4K 43 inch KD-43X7500F\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/1942/158930/tivi-sony-kd-43x7500f-5.jpg\" /></p>\n<h3>Điều khiển tivi bằng điện thoại th&ocirc;ng qua ứng dụng&nbsp;<a title=\"Video &amp; TV SideView\" href=\"https://www.die